
•	Gradle
1.	 
•	Core Concepts
Concepts	What it means
Build	指项目构建的过程与环境，一次构建包含一个或者多个项目以及其构建脚本
Project	需要构建的项目或者库
Task	基本的构建工作单元，例如编译compiling或者运行测试running tests. Task在构建脚本中声名或者在插件中添加
Build Script	构建脚本，即build.gradle(.kts)，用于定义task，dependency以及其他构建Project的指令……
Plugin	插件用于扩展Gradle的功能，比如tasks和规范conventions
Dependency	内部外部的资源，被Project所依赖
	




•	Gradle structure
 

•	Gradle Wrapper
1.	 
2.	The Gradle Wrapper is the script called gradlew(macOS) or gradlew.bat(windows)
3.	We use Gradle Wrapper by calling ./gradlew build(macOS) instead of using gradle build
The Wrapper invokes a declared version of Gradle, downloading it beforehand if necessary.
 


•	Use Gradle Wrapper to build Gradle Project
o	If based on Windows
	Run gradlew.bat build
o	If based on MacOS
	Run ./gradlew build







